plain ubuntu does not support project description

project(friclient VERSION 1.0.0
        LANGUAGES C CXX
)

in src/friUdpConnection.cpp, HAVE_SOCKLEN_T is not defined for ubuntu. Has to be set in cmake somehow

#ifdef HAVE_SOCKLEN_T
      socklen_t sockAddrSize;
#else
      int sockAddrSize;
#endif

Add -Wall flag to silence warnings, e.g. https://stackoverflow.com/questions/14231292/cmake-and-compiler-warnings

if ( CMAKE_COMPILER_IS_GNUCC )
    target_compile_options(main PRIVATE "-Wall -Wextra")
endif()
if ( MSVC )
    target_compile_options(main PRIVATE "/W4")
endif()

not possible, however, maybe changes depending on compile flags, given by initial build strategy


installed to /user/local

build with
cmake -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH='/usr/local' ..
make

execute with ./lbrjointsineoverlay

Network

System Settings -> Network -> Wired -> Options -> IPv4 Settings -> Address 172.31.1.148 Netmask 255.255.0.0
